Description:
63mm (2.5 Inch) Circular Aluminium Flush Joint Downpipe x 3m

Colonnade Round Flushfit Aluminium Downpipe x 3m are available in Mill Finish and in PPC (Polyester Powder Coating).

ARP Flushjoint Circular Aluminium Downpipes are avalible in a range of pipe sizes (63mm, 76mm and 101mm) and are supplied with a complete range of fittings such as bends, branches, offsets and various brackets.

The Collonade Range of Downpipes Offer Various Styles of Rainwater Goods Including Circular, Square And rectangular Pipe Ideal for any property, from modern to traditional and equally suited for refurbishment of Heritage or Listed properties.

The Hidden Spigots of The Design Give A Smooth External Finish, Alongside The Lightweight and Easy to Install Design Provides A Great Rainwater Solution.

To see standard polyester powder colours avalible in this range, please click the ARP Colours Options tab above.&nbsp;

Please note - allow 10 working days for delivery of Painted options. All PPC items are coated external face only.

Please note - If purchasing polyester powder coated goods, please type your colour selection in the delivery notes.

All aluminium Downpipes and fittings are specially ordered and are non-returnable.

Life Expectancy: 30 Years&nbsp;

Manufacturer: ARP (Aluminium Roofline Products)&nbsp;

Product Code: 2RFDP3&nbsp;

